description: [``botocore``] With this release, ElastiCache customers will be able to use predefined metricType "ElastiCacheDatabaseCapacityUsageCountedForEvictPercentage" for their ElastiCache instances.
[``botocore``] Add PollingDisabledAt time information in PipelineMetadata object of GetPipeline API.
[``botocore``] GameLift FleetIQ users can now filter game server claim requests to exclude servers on instances that are draining.

[``botocore``] Added ability to create data quality rulesets for shared, cross-account Glue Data Catalog tables. Added support for dataset comparison rules through a new parameter called AdditionalDataSources. Enhanced the data quality results with a map containing profiled metric values.

[``botocore``] This SDK update allows for path parameter syntax to be passed to the CreateRoute API. Path parameter syntax require parameters to be enclosed in {} characters. This update also includes a new AppendSourcePath field which lets users forward the source path to the Service URL endpoint.
[``botocore``] Amazon SageMaker Automatic Model Tuning now supports enabling Autotune for tuning jobs which can choose tuning job configurations.
